data.description: This home is eligible for the Buyers Advantage with 100% financing and no MI conventional portfolio loan program. Luxurious living awaits in this newly built (2021) 3 bed 2.5 bath townhome with 1813 sq ft of living space plus a 2 car (attached) garage and a covered back patio. Floor plan is mostly open and features vaulted ceilings. Kitchen on main level is light, bright and boasts granite counter tops, SS appliances (no refrigerator). Master bedroom conveniently located on main level also, which includes spacious private bathroom with a walk in shower, dual sinks, a walk-in closet, plus a separate linen/storage closet. Separate half bath located on the main level for guests and convenience as well. Upstairs leads to a bonus space ideal for den, office, etc, plus 2 more bedrooms and a full bathroom. Back yard has a white vinyl privacy fence that continuously runs across the back of the property. The community offers residents options of outdoor fun with a dog park, play ground, tennis courts and more with low HOA. HOA includes: cable, internet AND LAWN service.  The location of Holiday is central to Tampa and beaches. Lots to see and do, many tourist attractions within an hour North or South of Holiday, as well as many conveniences and necessities too!
